          <li><a href="/blog/wealth-building-habits">Wealth Building Habits</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/money-mindset-shift">Money Mindset Shift</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="external-resources">
        <h3>Further Reading</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://www.investopedia.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Investopedia</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.psychologytoday.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Psychology Today</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="book-recommendations">
        <h3>Recommended Books</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><em>The Psychology of Money</em> by Morgan Housel</li>
          <li><em>Rich Dad Poor Dad</em> by Robert Kiyosaki</li>
